Package com.microsoft.tfs.core.config

Interface Summary
ConnectionAdvisor A ConnectionAdvisor provides services and configuration data for a TFSConnection to use.
 

Class Summary
ConnectionInstanceData A holder class for TFSTeamProjectCollection instance configuration data.
DefaultConnectionAdvisor The default ConnectionAdvisor implementation.
EnvironmentVariables A collection of all the environment variables that control configuration in classes in the com.microsoft.tfs.core.config package.
RegistryUtils A collection methods for using the Windows registry to load and store core configuration settings.
 

Exception Summary
IllegalConfigurationException Thrown when information provided to a configuration class was invalid, or the configuration could not be completed.
